            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Hd1e108">Rubrica 13</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De facti probatione et testimonio</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>
      ¶ De facti probatione et 
               te<lb ed="#V" n="67" break="no"/>stimonio. Rubrica. 13
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e118">IN exodo c 20.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e125">No 
               lo<lb ed="#V" n="69" break="no"/>queris contra 
               pro<lb ed="#V" n="70" break="no"/>ximum tuum falsum testimonium.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e133">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e132">In libro numeri c. pe.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e137">Ad vnius
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>testimonium nullus condemnabitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e144">
               <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e145">Moyses in deute. c. 19.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e148">Non stabit testis
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>vnus contra aliquem: quicquid illud 
               pec<lb ed="#V" n="75" break="no"/>cati et facinoris fuerit: sed in ore duorum aut
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>trium testium stat omne verbum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e161">Salomon in prouerb. c. 19.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e162">Testis falsus
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>non erit impunitus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e168">
               <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e173">Aristoteles retho. li. i. c. 25. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e172">Nihil 
               mi<lb ed="#V" n="80" break="no"/>nus coacti falsa dicunt quam vera: et pertinaces non
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>dicere vera: et facile mentientes tanquam 
               requi<lb ed="#V" n="82" break="no"/>escituri sceleris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHy6yh-d44168-d1e182">
               <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e189">Tullius rethori. artis noue libro. 2 ca 2.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e186">Uita hominis ex antefactis spectabitur. 
               Argu<lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>mentum est per quod res coarguitur certioribus
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>argumentis: et magis firma suspitione. A quo
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>sit factum maleficium hoc modo spectabitur:
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>si telum: si vestimentum: si quid eiusmodi reli <!--143.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="58-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1" break="no"/>ctum: aut si vestigium rei repertum fuerit: aut
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>cruor in vestimentis: aut si in eo loco 
               compre<lb ed="#V" n="3" break="no"/>hensus: aut vsus transacto negocio: quo in 
               lo<lb ed="#V" n="4" break="no"/>co res gesta dicitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e210"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e221">Libro. 4. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e212">Oportet 
               te<lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>stimonium cum re conuenire: aliter enim rem non
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>potest confirmare.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e220"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e233">Idem topicorum. ca. 24 et
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>fi</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e222">Testimonium dicimus omne quod ab aliqua
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>re externa sumitur ad faciendum fidem. 
               Perso<lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>na non qualiscumque est testimonii pondus 
               ha<lb ed="#V" n="10" break="no"/>bet: ad fidem enim faciendam auctoritas queritur.
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>Auctoritas in virtute inest maxima. Plerum
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>que creditur his qui experti sunt. Per somnum:
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>vnum: insaniam: multa sepe patefacta sunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e241">
               <lb ed="#V" n="14"/> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e260">Idem inuectiuarum in catilinam li. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e245">Quid 
               ex<lb ed="#V" n="15" break="no"/>pectas auctoritatem loquentium: quorum 
               volunta<lb ed="#V" n="16" break="no"/>tem tacitorum perspicis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e254"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e272">Idem inuectiua in 
               salu<lb ed="#V" n="17" break="no"/>stium:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e256">Ubi res testimonia assunt quid opus
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>est verbis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e264">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e287">Ouidius sine titulo seu amorum libro i. c. 10.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e268">Nec bene conducti vendunt periuria testes.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e274">
               <lb ed="#V" n="21"/> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e298">Libro. 2. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e278">Culpa nec ex facili quamuis
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>manifesta probatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e284">
               <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e310">Paulus apostolus epistola ad corinthios. c. 13 et
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e288">In ore duorum vel trium testium stat omne verbum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e294">
               <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e323">Seneca in prouerb.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e298">Fatetur facinus qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>iudicium fugit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e304">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e336">Auctor li. de forma honeste vite. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e308">
               Testi<lb ed="#V" n="28" break="no"/>monium veritati non amicitie reddas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e315">
               <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e348">Cato. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e319">Productus testis salua tamen
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>ante pudorem.
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>Quantumcumque potes: celato crimen amici.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-d1e327">
               <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Rd1e362">Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 5. e. 39.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d44168-Qd1e331">Quanto
        <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>vehementior pena est: tanto eius rei debet 
               in<lb ed="#V" n="34" break="no"/>quisitio plus haberi: ne amore vindicte 
               inno<lb ed="#V" n="35" break="no"/>centes videantur vite pericula sustinere.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
